## Local Services (Coming Soon)

**Revenue timeline:** 30-60 days | **Startup cost:** $0-200

These are service-based but location-dependent:
- Home Services (house cleaning, landscaping, handyman)
- Childcare & Education (nannying, tutoring, babysitting)
- Pet Services (dog walking, grooming, training)
- Beauty & Wellness (hair, nails, massage)
- Event Services (photography, catering, planning)

---

## Physical Products (Coming Soon)

**Revenue timeline:** 60-120 days | **Startup cost:** $100-1K

Create and sell physical goods:
- Handmade crafts (Etsy)
- Print-on-demand (no inventory)
- Private label products
- Reselling & dropshipping

---

## Rental & Resale (Coming Soon)

**Revenue timeline:** 30-60 days | **Startup cost:** $1K-5K

Generate passive income by renting or reselling items:
- Equipment rental (cameras, tools, party supplies)
- Furniture & home décor resale
- Vehicle sharing (Turo)
- Storage space rental (Neighbor.com)

